OL,3,CStarmer's Government returns to
OL,4,CWestminster amid leadership rivals'
OL,5,CBrexit row
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer's Government will
OL,8,Freturn to Westminster after a battle
OL,9,Fover reversing Brexit was ignited
OL,10,Famong the rivals vying to oust him as
OL,11,FPrime Minister.
OL,13,FWes Streeting, who resigned as health
OL,14,Fsecretary last week, signalled he
OL,15,Fwanted to see Britain return to the EU
OL,16,Fas he announced on Saturday he would
OL,17,Fstand in any Labour leadership contest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
