CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779117068
OL,3,CStarmer's Government returns to
OL,4,CWestminster amid leadership rivals'
OL,5,CBrexit row
OL,7,FSupporters of Andy Burnham are
OL,8,Freportedly furious with Mr Streeting,
OL,9,Faccording to the Times, as they
OL,10,Fbelieve it is a deliberate attempt to
OL,11,Fraise the salience of Brexit in the
OL,12,Fleave-voting constituency of
OL,13,FMakerfield, where the Greater
OL,14,FManchester Mayor hopes to stand as a
OL,15,Fparliamentary candidate.
OL,17,FMr Burnham sought to play down his own
OL,18,Fsupport for rejoining the trade bloc
OL,19,Fas he took part in a media blitz
OL,20,Facross the weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779117068
OL,3,CStarmer's Government returns to
OL,4,CWestminster amid leadership rivals'
OL,5,CBrexit row
OL,7,FHe insisted there was a "long-term
OL,8,Fcase" for advocating to join the EU,
OL,9,Fbut insisted he was not campaigning on
OL,10,Fthat issue in the by-election.
OL,12,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy rebuked
OL,13,Fher former colleague, Mr Streeting,
OL,14,Ffor making Europe a centre-point of
OL,15,Fhis campaign to succeed Sir Keir,
OL,16,Fdescribing it as "odd".
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@EO]xD@ROUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779117068
OL,3,CStarmer's Government returns to
OL,4,CWestminster amid leadership rivals'
OL,5,CBrexit row
OL,7,F"If rejoining the EU is the answer,
OL,8,Fthen essentially what we're saying to
OL,9,Fpeople is, 'life was fine in 2015, we
OL,10,Fjust need to go back there'," added Ms
OL,11,FNandy, who is seen as an ally to the
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Mayor.
OL,14,FReform UK, which is the second placed
OL,15,Fparty in Makerfield, plans to make hay
OL,16,Fout of Mr Burnham's previous support
OL,17,Ffor rejoining the EU as it knocks
OL,18,Fdoors in the constituency.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
