OL,3,CStarmer's Government returns to
OL,4,CWestminster amid leadership rivals'
OL,5,CBrexit row
OL,7,FShe later added: "So, I wouldn't write
OL,8,Foff the Prime Minister, but I would
OL,9,Fjust say that this is a very personal
OL,10,Fdecision.
OL,12,F"He's got to make that decision
OL,13,Fhimself."
OL,15,FElsewhere 'amid' the turmoil at the
OL,16,Fheart of government:
OL,26,@oD@ROUtD@AOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
