OL,3,CStarmer's Government returns to
OL,4,CWestminster amid leadership rivals'
OL,5,CBrexit row
OL,7,F` Chancellor Rachel Reeves is expected
OL,8,Fto shelve plans to hike fuel duty by
OL,9,F5p per litre, amid concerns about the
OL,10,Fimpact of the Iran war on the cost of
OL,11,Fliving, several media reports claimed.
OL,12,FThe Treasury would not comment on
OL,13,Fspeculation.
OL,15,F` Angela Rayner turned down the
OL,16,Fposition of health secretary after Mr
OL,17,FStreeting left the post, The Times
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
