OL,3,CStarmer's Government returns to
OL,4,CWestminster amid leadership rivals'
OL,5,CBrexit row
OL,7,F` Outgoing Makerfield MP Josh Simons
OL,8,Fdenied reports he decided to give his
OL,9,Fseat up for Mr Burnham a year ago. Mr
OL,10,FSimons told the BBC he made the
OL,11,Fdecision "two days ago", after
OL,12,Fdiscussing it with his wife.
